<P>
JK:  Yes.  All these global outbreaks of nationalism seem to me to be such
a clear response to technology.  Once you see it this way, these things are
so simple.
<P>
B:  And irrelevant.  Oh, that's part of that.
<P>

JK:  Yes.  And politics.  People ask are you a democrat or a republican?  I
