<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/censorship_big_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Censorship - Internet Censorship Legislation &amp; Regulation (CDA, etc.)&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Censorship/Internet_censorship_bills/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Mon Dec 16 17:52:28 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
