<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases - EF-Georgia, EFF, ACLU, et al. v. Gov. &amp; Atty. Gen. of Georgia (State)&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/EFGA_v_GA/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Sep 25 16:11:44 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="#files">Files</A></TD><h6></h6>
<TD><A HREF="#dirs">Subdirectories</A></TD><h6></h6>
