<DOCOLDNO>IA080-000555-B016-201</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/pub/Net_info/EFF_Net_Guide/Other_versions/French/HTML_version/chap6.html 204.253.162.4 19970103103151 text/html 56412
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 10:31:51 GMT
