    Hutchison explaining that she will review the text of the CDA before 
    forming an opinion
<DT><a href="s314_hr1004_post_eff.analysis"><B>s314_hr1004_post_eff.analysis</B></a>
<DD>EFF policy paper on the original CDA
<DT><a href="s314_hr1004_s652.alert"><B>s314_hr1004_s652.alert</B></a>
<DD>Alert from EFF, VTW, CDT and others re CDA
    (updated frequently)
<DT><a href="s314_most_95.commentary"><B>s314_most_95.commentary</B></a>
