    Internet: The Democratization of Mass Media and the Emerging Paradigm of Cyberspace.</A> 
<DT>Cybersociology Newsgroups (Note:only available to you if your site 
carries them!) 
<DL>
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.2600">alt.2600</A> Hierarchy
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.comp.acad-freedom">alt.comp.academic-freedom</A>
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.comp.acad-freedom.talk">alt.comp.acad-freedom.talk</A>
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.comp.acad-freedom.news">alt.comp.acad-freedom.news</A>
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.culture.internet">alt.culture.internet</A>
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.culture.usenet">alt.culture.usenet</A>
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.cyberpunk">alt.cyberpunk</A>
  <DT><A HREF="news:alt.cyberpunk.movement">alt.cyberpunk.movement</A>
